premise_source_doc_sentence: Jane Watts or Jane Waldie  (  1793 -- 1826  )  was a Scottish artist and author .

Janice Robinson  (  born 8 December 1967  )  is an American vocalist , initially known as a member of Livin ' Joy before she pursued on her solo career .
Her biggest hit with Livin ' Joy was reissued with new production , and new vocals and Janice was credited for her work on it this time .
It ushered in a new vocalist after the group failed to reach a deal with Janice Robinson , the original vocalist on their number 1 smash `` Dreamer '' .
Previously Janice Robinson was the soulful sultry powerhouse vocalist whose strengths also included songwriting  (  she wrote `` Dreamer ''  )  .
